data.description: Check out this Huge Split Foyer with over 2800 Htd Sq. Ft. that includes 5 Bedrooms/4 Full baths!  Vaulted ceilings and Large open Living room.  Huge Kitchen with new counter tops and Smart Lighting.  Oversized Garage with workshop/storage space.  Bonus room on lower level.  Large deck with salt water above ground pool.  Wired for hot tub on deck.  New floors on main along with new tiled Master bath in 2022.  Roof replaced in 2020.  Storage area lower level set up for wood burning stove.  Located in Great Neighborhood and 5 mins from King!
